{
  "texts": [
    "In this article, we will introduce many eye tracking tools that tackle a wide range of problems.",
    "This includes tools for data recording and cleaning, classification of fixations and other events, and to generate areas-of-interest and conduct analyses with them.",
    "We will not deliver a ready-to-use pipeline for conducting eye tracking research in this article, since we do not believe there is a one-size-fits-all solution.",
    "Nor do we aim to provide an exhaustive list of tools.",
    "The aim of this article is to improve the level of individual eye tracking researchers and their operation."
  ]
}